divs: Sighting DetailsTwo boys crossing a footbridge over a creek observed two bright lightsapproaching from the distance at treetop level, criss-crossing the creek as ifsearching. As the lights moved slowly (walking speed) and silently overhead,they detected a dark undetermined shape blocking the stars. The object continuedto follow the creek until lost from view.
trends: There have been 5 other sightings in Minnetonka

Summary: Dark shape following a creek in MN.
